<h1>Welcome <%=@user.name%>!!!</h1>

<h2>I sure do hope you like our company!<br>Here is your info!</h2>

<h3>Your dentist is currently <%=@user.dentist.name%>.<br>
<%=@user.dentist.name%> charges and estimated $<%=@user.dentist.fee%> per visit. <br>
<%=@user.insurance.company%> reduces that price by $<%=@user.insurance.coverage%><br><br>

This brings your estimated Co-Pay to <%=(@user.dentist.fee) - (@user.insurance.coverage)%>!</h3>

<%if session[:developer?]%>
  <form action="/dentists" method="get">
    <input type="submit" value="Developer Options" class="button">
  </form><br><br>
<%end%>

<form action="/user/<%=session[:user_id]%>/edit" method="get">
  <input type="submit" name="" value="Edit Info" class="button">
</form><br><br>

<form action="/dentists" method="get">
  <input type="submit" name="" value="Shop Dentists" class="button">
</form><br><br>

<form action="/user/<%=session[:user_id]%>/delete" method="get">
  <input type="submit" value="Delete Acct" class="button">
</form>
